title: Scott Lafaro - 1958 - West Coast Days
description:
Import release featuring vintage live recordings from the Lighthouse in Hermosa Beach, CA. 

Shelly Manne and His Men, featuring Gordon, Kamuca, Russ Freeman (p) and Monte Budwig (b) play Our Delight (inc), 

Summertime and Poinciana (July, 1960) while Kamuca, LaFaro, Victor Feldman (p) and Stan Levy (dr) play Paul&#039;s Pal (mistitled It Could Happen to You) and Bass Blues (September 1958).
